## GMAIL
IMAPAccount gmail
Host imap.gmail.com
User <%= @mail.mail %>
AuthModule /media/s3ql/<%= @mail.mail %>/xoauth.sh
UseIMAPS yes


IMAPStore gmail-remote
Account gmail


MailDirStore local
AltMap no
Path <%= @maildir %>
Inbox <%= @maildir %>/Inbox


Channel gmail-local
Master :gmail-remote:
Slave  :local:
Create Slave
Sync Pull
Patterns *
# SyncState *
